                                    <p style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; color:#000000; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;"><strong style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">Hi,</strong></p>
                                    <p class="justify" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; color:#000000; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="justify">The <a href="http://fossee.in" target="_blank" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #2BA6CB; margin: 0; padding: 0;">FOSSEE</a> project based at IIT Bombay invites the faculty, students and members of your institution / organization to <a href="http://fossee.in/conference/cfd-symposium" target="_blank" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #2BA6CB; margin: 0; padding: 0;">OpenFOAM Symposium 2016</a>.</p>
                                    <center><a href="http://fossee.in/conference/cfd-symposium/" target="_blank"><img width="200" height="200" src="http://fossee.in/data/emails/images/cfd_openfoam_logo.png" alt= "cfd-openfoam 2015" /></a></center>
                                    <center><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 40px; color: #84B839; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify;" >OpenFOAM Symposium</span></center>
                                    <center>
                                        <hr style=" border: 0; height: 2px; background-image:-moz-linear-gradient(left center , #FFF, #84B839, #FFF);background-image:-webkit-linear-gradient(left, #fff, #84B839, #fff);" ></hr>
                                        
                                    </center>
                                    <center><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; color: #84B839; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify;" >27 February 2016 | LCH, IIT Bombay</span></center>
                                    <br style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;" />
                                    <p class="justify" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; color:#000000; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="justify">OpenFOAM is a free and open source Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) toolbox which is used widely 
in the field of engineering, both in industry and academia.</p>
                                    <p class="justify" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; color:#000000; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;" align="justify">The Free and Open Source Software for Education (FOSSEE) team at IIT Bombay is conducting a one day symposium on  OpenFOAM. The main objective of the symposium is to facilitate the interaction between 
experts in the field of OpenFOAM and the beginners. The symposium will feature talks and discussion by
the eminent users and developers of OpenFOAM from both industry and academia.</p>
                                    <!-- Callout Panel -->
